  "body": "## Issue\r\n\r\nTruffle tries to execute the vyper compiler, even if there are no vyper sources present. If truffle finds any `.json` file, it assumes that the project contains vyper code and tries to run the vyper compiler. \r\n\r\n@cameel did an analyses here: https://github.com/ethereum/solidity/pull/10672#issuecomment-749699412.",
